Right on the side of the homepage. - <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1597877609" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;">LurkD</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
