</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>Has been discussed numerous times, see most recent discussion:<br />
<a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/forum/t-1786517/scp-names-in-page-titles#post-2868550">http://05command.wikidot.com/forum/t-1786517/scp-names-in-page-titles#post-2868550</a> - <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1597877609" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;">LurkD</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>I would add a method to go from one SCP to the next. Like a &quot;Previous/Next&quot; button.</li>
<li>Navigation buttons for the SCP : Previous, Next, Random, First, Last</li>
<li>Add a button that sends you to the next SCP article instead of having to go back to the list of SCP's and try to find where you just were.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p>Being worked on currently, see recent discussion:<br />
<a href="http://05command.wikidot.com/forum/t-2259687/back-next-buttons">http://05command.wikidot.com/forum/t-2259687/back-next-buttons</a> - <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1500566&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1597877609" alt="LurkD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1500566)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1500566); return false;">LurkD</a></span></p>
