<li>Maybe add more futuristic look.</li>
<li>How about adding something a bit more aesthetic. Something that tops the page that grips the viewer and sucks them in. Have you ever seen something so odd and out of place that you catch yourself just staring stupidly at it?</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
